metadata.description: Masonic Premium is our first-ever collection. Limited collection of 333 unique premium NFTs, with numerous benefits and utilities for the future; your digital passport to our Masonic Temple in the Metaverse, gaming experiences and exclusive discounts. The Aprentice Scottish Rite Aquarius #1 NFT holder will have exclusive access to the Masonic Temple and 10% discount in our Masonic Temple Store.
